<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>HoneyCombo</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/src/css/login.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-Gn5384xqQ1aoWXA+058RXPxPg6fy4IWvTNh0E263XmFcJlSAwiGgFAW/dAiS6JXm" crossorigin="anonymous">
</head>

<body>
    <header>
        <div class="container d-flex mt-2">
            <div class="p-2">
                <a href="main">
                    <div class='logo-wrapper'>
                        <img class='img-fluid' src="/static/logo.png" width="200" height="70">
                    </div>
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="p-2">
                <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light">
                    <a class="p-3 text-dark ml-5 mr-5" style="text-decoration: none" href="/product/main"><h2>상품</h2></a>
                    <a class="p-3 text-dark ml-3" style="text-decoration: none" href="/recipe/mainRecipe"><h2>레시피</h2></a>
                </nav>
            </div>
            <div class="ml-auto p-4 mt-2">
                <a class="btn btn-primary" id="login" href="/auth/login">로그인</a>
                <a class="btn btn-primary" id="signup" href="/auth/signup">회원가입</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>
    <main>
        <section class="jumbotron" style="height: 230px;">
        </section>
        <h2 class="text-center">꿀조합러가 될 준비되셨나요?</h2>
        <h2 class="text-center">환영합니다 ^0^</h2>
        <hr>
        <div class="signupcenter">
            <div class="login">
                <p class="loginword"><h2>회원가입</h2></p>
                <form action="/auth/signup" method="post">
                    <input class="logininput" type="text" placeholder="아이디를 입력해주세요" name="ID" style="margin-top: 10px;" /> <br />
                    <input class="logininput" type="password" placeholder="비밀번호를 입력해주세요" name="PW" /> <br />
                    <div class="logResult"><%= message %></div>
                    <input class="loginBtn" type="submit" value="가입하기">
                </form>
            </div>
            <p class="gomain"><button class="mainbutton" type="button" onclick="location.href='/product/main'">홈으로</button>
            </p>
        </div>
    </main>
</body>

</html>